Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NJango!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of Miss\NKaya like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have her write her butler\Ninto her will. Then kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NStay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NLuffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Usopp are gonna chase\Ndown that hypno freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUsopp, Zoro! Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You cocky jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's Captain\NKuro for ya'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering, laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't call\Nme that! You fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole plan was devised
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I may be rid of\Nthat name once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Concocting plans everyday for\Na bunch of barbarians who care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,only about havoc and mayhem!\NRelentlessly attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by government dogs\Nand bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sick and tired of\Nthat entire cursed life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I've been toughening\Nmyself up to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want a reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just greedy, Kuro.\NBut I have ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Protect Kaya! The Usopp\NPirate's Great Efforts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Onion, is that weird hypnotist\Nguy still behind us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know I can't\Nsee him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure and\Nlose him for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that nut job
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,could catch up to us\Nin our own forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NDon't you worry, Miss Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usopp Pirates are gonna\Nkeep you safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] That's right! The Usopp\NPirates stand by their word!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWell, they're not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools, I'm coming to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\Nyou can run from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWe could do this the easy way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or I could just level\Nthis entire forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NWhoa! That guy is really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] And he can do a lot\Nmore than just hypnotize people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CARROT] Ah-ah-ah...!\N--[PEPPER, ONION gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Come out, come\Nout, wherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go east! Hey, I said go east!\NSo go east already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the wrong direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Fine, east.\NIs that left or right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NTurn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NBut that's where we came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] I'm sorry.\NYou should go on with out me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are under strict\Norders to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] Oh no!\NShe's got a really bad fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NWhat?! Hang in there Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor! We need a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] You idiot!\NWe don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's tryin' to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] But it's dangerous\Nfor her to run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NYeah but--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NShow yourselves, you runts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NThank you... for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the thought is more than\Nenough. Now go, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you brats go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use running!\NCome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, CARROT, ONION whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] If we left Kaya\Nand ran away right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we would probably\Nsurvive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NYeah. Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] And our Captain\Nalways said to run
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with your tail between your legs\Nif you think you're gonna lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Those brats\Nthink they can mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, our\Ncaptain is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But even he didn't\Ntake his own advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried so hard to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He risked his life for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT sighs]\NI swore to protect Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] All right then! Prepare\Nyourselves, Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NWe gotta fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NLet's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this! You're no match\Nfor him, you're only kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't put your life\Non the line for my sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't wanna die, we\Nhave to fight for our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NUh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] Just like our\Ncaptain always said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! He just--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He just broke Captain\NKuro's "cat claw".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] That leaves only five\Nmore of those weird swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A] Don't worry guys!\NHe can still fight plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G] Yeah! He still\Nhas that other claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! Rip that guy\Nto shreds, Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NDon't use that name anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in this village his\Nname is Klaha... something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Klaha-something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Klaha-something!\NGet him good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NShut your mouths! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NSoon enough I'll deal with you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the only\Nappropriate manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Extermination! I'll also\Nkill that fool Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why kill us, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon please don't joke around\Nlike that Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE O]\NIt's still not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to attack\Nthe village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Captain Jango gets\Nher to write her will,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,then your plan should\Nstill work perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan is no longer\Nany of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When all of you are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this village will know who\Nto blame for this atrocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] I never intended\Nto let any of you mongrels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,leave this village alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No one... No one who\Nknows my true identity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can be allowed to live\Nto tell about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You had already planned to\Nkill every last one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO chuckles]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago I planned\Nto erase Captain Kuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and every last person\Nwho ever knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all part of\Nmy plan! [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou guys are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most uncool\Npirates I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. We're "uncool", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are nothing\Nmore than savages,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,incapable of rising above\Ntheir animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my plans, what could\Nthey possibly accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A crew is nothing to me. They\Nare simply a means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Crewmembers are just\Npawns in the Captain's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether my men live or die\Nis up to me and me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell them to fight,\Nthey will fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I order them to die,\Nthey had better do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They know the punishment\Nfor disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThis is how pirates are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare talk\Ndown to me, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES murumur]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] You know, no\Nmatter how many hundreds,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or thousands of men follow\Nyou as their Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never be\Nas good as Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool. Are you\Nsaying that I am inferior
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to a kid pretending\Nto be a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Well aren't you\Nfunny?! Don't get all cocky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just because you snapped\Noff one of my cat claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly is he better\Nthan me?! Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause he's got heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHe's got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] A guy like you doesn't\Nknow what a true pirate is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES stammer]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NImpossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] He kept up with\Nthe pussyfoot maneuver!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHow insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] It would appear\Nthat you need a lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in what real pirates are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first lesson\Nwill be about terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A lesson I learned well\Nas I stared down death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Should he be\Nin that stance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE X] Why's he\Nusing that technique?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE DD]\NHe's only fighting one guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to use the\NOut of the Back Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE X]\NThis isn't a good spot for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he could get us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M] Yeah. He did say he\Nwas gonna kill us all earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE DD] Please Captain Kuro!\NAnything but that technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NWe'll do anything, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE X]\NPlease, Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? He's just\Nwobbling back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES begging]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're begging you,\NCaptain! Let us live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NOut of the Back Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]\NWhat a small haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I really thought they'd\Nhave more treasure than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if the boys have\Nfinished this fight yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What...? Everyone\Nhas stopped... Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE EE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NThat guy's everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this Captain!\NPlease stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't reason with him\Nnow that he's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His sidestep maneuver is so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,not even he knows\Nwhat he's cutting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could he have killed\Nso many of us without even--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--[groans]\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat's happening out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People are just getting\Ncut to ribbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming, groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShow yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any honor?!\NThose men are your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY panting]\NI found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've accepted\Nyour fate like a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my little pawns\Nare still alive, and in misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been better to\Njust let them die in the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] So, now what?\NDo you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never be like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NNot "will".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,can't be like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to die here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, you'll\Nwrithe in agony
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as I hack you up like a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to carve you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the Back Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out you brats!\NI know you're hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give yourselves up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] We surrender!\NWe'll hand her over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, and we'll take\Nyou to her! Just don't kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm stupid?\NI won't fall for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You silly rug rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOh, dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We got him...! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NPepper Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO sneezes]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO sneezes]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those worthless brats were\Nlying to me from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL grunting]\NPush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOYS]\NEnd of the line, hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, CARROT yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOYS groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Looks like you bit off a\Nlittle more than you could chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NNo! We failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NReal pirates don't take kindly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to being mocked by\Nthe likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NOnion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] You pretend pirates\Nsure got in over your heads,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich girl, I know you're here!\NListen! Unless you show yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll execute these\Nthree little lambs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will make sure to do it\Nin a most painful fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not doubt my skill\Nat such a task!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NMiss Kaya! Run for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey!\N--Yeah. That's them all aright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThey're the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, leave the children\Nbe. I'll write the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna kill you as soon\Nas you write that will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl. Don't you know\Nyou can't bargain with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro specifically\Ninstructed me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to get rid of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOYS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do exactly as I say\Nthen you won't get to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and, I won't write my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NHold on! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down!\NDon't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely have to get\Nyou to write that will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Fine, I'll let\Nthe little brats go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in their condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't be making\Ntoo quick of a getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NDon't forget to sign your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOYS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO chuckles] "I leave my\Nentire fortune to my butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore," Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good! This is your will,\Nall right! Excellent work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now remember, we had a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me you\Nwouldn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax. I know I\Nmay not look like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm regarded\Nas an honest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION, CARROT]\NKaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZORO] Okay! I'll be back!\N--[USOPP] What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that,\Nhypno-freak! Let the girl go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Damnit! Looks\Nlike I was followed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'd better finish off\Nthe rich girl quickly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] All finished here!\NThe rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I won't lose to someone\Nwho ditches his name
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and runs from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.97,0:24:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember my name for\Nthe rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.77,0:24:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I hate him!\NThat man is scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's what pirates are like!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.36,0:24:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] That's not\Nwhat friends are like!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger explosion!\NKuro vs. Luffy, how it ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates!

